Package: ShinyWeather
Title: A Shiny app to show the weather in a child-friendly way
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
  person(given = "Magda",
  family = "Matetovici", 
  email = "magda.matetovici@yahoo.com", 
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description:
  This app will show the weather in a Shiny app in a friendly manner for children. It will show temperature, wind, chances of rain. Depending on the temperature, wind and rain it will show a picture of what can be done outside which can be refreshed to give several ideas.
